### Enterprise RAG Platform — REST Client Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### Place a sample PDF as ./sample.pdf or update the path below

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Document Upload
### Replace ./sample.pdf with the path to your test PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Chat with the uploaded document
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "what is this document about?"
}
